{"title":"牛的雕塑","authors":["燎原"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":8,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛的雕塑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燎原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一尊炭红色的牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我的案头，拱起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成一架沉默的山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一个需要英雄的午夜或拂晓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它从黑色的土地上缓缓站起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"痛苦使它硕壮头颅低垂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使命造就了它的个性：肩胛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高出于一切痛苦之上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有部位都绷成负荷的力点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直至颈项，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直至抠进土地中粗短的四肢……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……冲决一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必然呼啸于大野之上的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是它额间的风！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}